Class InflectionRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nih.nlm.nls.lvg.Trie.InflectionRule

  • public class InflectionRule
extends java.lang.Object
    This class creates an object of LVG inflection rule, using a string format of a rule. The string format of a rule is described in the design document

        public void Reverse()
        Reverse entities for inputs and outputs for a inflection rule. All nflection rules are bi-directional and stored on both cases while it was read in (once).
